Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.29,0:00:05.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mizuha membunuh ibunya, Izumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.04,0:00:10.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, Izumi masih hidup.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.80,0:00:12.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau dari mana saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.88,0:00:14.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sudah sarapan?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.97,0:00:20.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu orang lain yang muncul\Ndi hadapan Fushi…
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.97,0:00:23.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau lebih tenang jika bersama Mizuha, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu juga yang diinginkan\Noleh wanita di belakangmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.33,0:02:07.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ibu Mizuha benar-benar di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.54,0:02:10.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan berisik.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.21,0:02:12.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.\NAku senang membawa Mizuha kemari.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.59,0:02:14.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang kita bisa menanyakan detailnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.34,0:02:18.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia Izumi, keturunan Hayase\Ndari Pasukan Pelindung.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.13,0:02:21.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tampaknya, Mizuha benar-benar\Nmenusuknya sampai mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.47,0:02:24.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kuduga.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.89,0:02:27.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu bagaimana dengan ibu Mizuha\Nyang masih hidup?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.77,0:02:29.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kukira dia CGI atau semacamnya…
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.35,0:02:31.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kuberi tahu teorinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.11,0:02:34.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sosok yang saat ini menjadi ibu Mizuha,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.27,0:02:35.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,identitas aslinya adalah…
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.32,0:02:37.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nokker.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.86,0:02:39.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak! Itu mustahil!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.74,0:02:41.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah menghabisi semua Nokker.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.99,0:02:44.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan Sosok Hitam bilang\Nmereka semua sudah musnah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.79,0:02:45.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.74,0:02:48.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, bagaimana jika kalian berdua\Ntidak menyadarinya?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.67,0:02:52.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkinkah Sosok Hitam seceroboh itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.54,0:02:55.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin ia sebenarnya cukup ceroboh.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.88,0:02:57.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.80,0:03:01.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Sosok Hitam! Seseorang meremehkanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.09,0:03:03.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keluar dan jelaskan padanya!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.39,0:03:07.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku benar, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.60,0:03:11.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu aneh. Ia tidak muncul belakangan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.35,0:03:14.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ia pasti malu. Abaikan saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejujurnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.23,0:03:18.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mizuha tinggal dengan peniru\Nsangat mengkhawatirkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.90,0:03:21.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, cepat hidupkan kembali Bu Izumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.20,0:03:24.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, Mizuha…
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.16,0:03:25.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.16,0:03:31.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah kau selalu bilang,\N"Lebih baik hidup"?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.46,0:03:33.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mizuha, maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.59,0:03:36.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan mencari cara.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.63,0:03:43.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aneh. Aku tak bisa\Nmenghidupkannya kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.43,0:03:47.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Biasanya, rohnya berdesir,\Nterisap ke dalam tubuh,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,lalu hidup kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.39,0:03:52.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.39,0:03:55.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkinkah karena peniru itu\Nmenggunakan tubuhnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.06,0:03:58.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Belum pernah ada kasus
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.36,0:04:02.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,saat jiwa asli tidak bisa kembali\Nke tubuhnya sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tubuh yang dikendalikan Nokker
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,hanyalah jasad yang bisa bergerak\Nmeski sudah mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.74,0:04:08.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ia bukan manusia sungguhan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.20,0:04:09.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika kita mengalahkan peniru itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.79,0:04:11.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,kita mungkin bisa memecahkan misteri ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.25,0:04:14.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, tolong sampaikan ini kepada Fushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.71,0:04:15.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beri tahu Mizuha
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.79,0:04:18.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,ibunya yang dahulu sudah tidak ada lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang dia lihat hari itu cuma mimpi buruk.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.51,0:04:23.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibunya yang saat ini di rumah\Nadalah ibunya yang asli.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.51,0:04:25.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong katakan itu padanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.64,0:04:26.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.01,0:04:29.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada yang harus kulakukan dalam wujud ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.68,0:04:31.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.64,0:04:33.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika itu benar-benar Nokker,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.39,0:04:36.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,artinya mereka telah berevolusi\Nsampai batas tertentu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.40,0:04:38.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di tempat yang tidak kita sadari,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.40,0:04:41.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,pasti ada orang lain yang berada\Ndalam situasi yang sama denganku.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.61,0:04:43.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika menemukan mereka,\Nkita mungkin mengetahui sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.20,0:04:45.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan keadaanku ini,\Naku bisa mencari orang seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.28,0:04:46.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bon, apa katanya?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.87,0:04:49.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong rahasiakan ini dari Mizuha.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.91,0:04:51.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini juga demi melindunginya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.75,0:04:54.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia dan aku akan mengumpulkan\Ninformasi sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.16,0:04:55.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami akan kabari jika ada sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.54,0:04:59.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai saat itu, tolong jaga Mizuha.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.38,0:05:00.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jaga…
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.71,0:05:03.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan buang waktu.\NAku mengandalkanmu mulai besok.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.76,0:05:06.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kuatur\Nagar kau satu kelas dengan Tonari.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.22,0:05:07.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau akan pergi ke sekolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.59,0:05:10.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hidup barumu menyenangkan, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.39,0:05:14.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Silakan masuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.23,0:05:22.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku Fushi. Senang bertemu kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.57,0:05:23.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rambutnya putih.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.94,0:05:25.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa dia orang asing?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.11,0:05:26.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia cukup tampan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.78,0:05:29.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bisa duduk di kursi kosong itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.66,0:05:30.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.58,0:05:31.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Oh"?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.58,0:05:32.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.50,0:05:36.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lupakan saja, aku akan mengajarimu nanti.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.33,0:05:38.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku Tonari.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.92,0:05:40.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Senang bertemu kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.34,0:05:41.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini kali pertamaku di sekolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.75,0:05:43.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuharap kita semua bisa akur.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.64,0:05:55.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana cara menggunakannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.69,0:05:57.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu…
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tekan seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.19,0:06:04.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, apa yang kalian lakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.19,0:06:08.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami meniru yang tertulis di sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.16,0:06:09.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu rupanya. Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.66,0:06:14.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini luar biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, itu murid pindahan yang dirumorkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.92,0:06:21.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga, dia keren sekali!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.50,0:06:24.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, dari mana asalmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.17,0:06:25.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Utara.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.34,0:06:26.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Negara mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.59,0:06:27.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entahlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.59,0:06:29.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.26,0:06:31.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Boleh kusentuh rambutmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.97,0:06:34.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Halus sekali!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.39,0:06:36.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Reaksi para gadis berlebihan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.56,0:06:38.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa salahnya? Biarkan saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.52,0:06:43.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga, kau ikut klub apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.36,0:06:45.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Klub?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.73,0:06:47.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami Klub Naginata.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.49,0:06:51.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mizuha, kau ikut klub apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.74,0:06:55.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ikut Klub Naginata,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.87,0:06:57.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi sudah berhenti.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.08,0:06:58.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau satu klub dengan Yuki sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mizuha.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.46,0:07:06.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kudengar kau pergi dengan juniormu kemarin.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.71,0:07:08.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa orang tuamu\Nsudah tidak terlalu keras padamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.72,0:07:10.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lantas, mari kita berkumpul lain kali.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.93,0:07:16.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.94,0:07:21.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan memikirkannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.48,0:07:22.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanna!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.02,0:07:26.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bersenang-senang di rumah Aoki?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.28,0:07:29.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu sangat menyenangkan.\NAda banyak orang di sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.49,0:07:32.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa aku sudah tahu siapa yang kau suka.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.49,0:07:34.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin! Jangan katakan itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.95,0:07:36.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena kau pasti akan salah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.79,0:07:40.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, aku tidak menduga ibumu\Nmengizinkanmu pergi ke rumah orang lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.00,0:07:45.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibuku tidak seperti dahulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.59,0:07:49.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di matamu, apa ibumu sempurna sekarang?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.38,0:07:52.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, ibuku sekarang adalah yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.30,0:07:56.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku penasaran apa pendapat ibumu\Njika dia mendengarmu mengatakan itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.01,0:07:59.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entahlah. Mungkin dia\Nakan menangis bahagia.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.39,0:08:03.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian bicara apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.48,0:08:05.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa dia murid pindahan itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.40,0:08:07.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia Fushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.52,0:08:09.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia yang disebutkan Aoki, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibumu pasti akan sedih.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.70,0:08:12.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.99,0:08:15.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau membahas itu sekarang?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.16,0:08:16.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mizuha.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.74,0:08:19.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, apa aku salah bicara?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.70,0:08:21.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini bukan salahmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bon, kenapa kau di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.25,0:08:28.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bekerja di sini untuk melindungimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.09,0:08:29.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang aku kakakmu\Nyang menjadi petugas kebersihan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keren, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.84,0:08:32.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.76,0:08:37.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bu Izumi, ibu Mizuha,\Nberterima kasih padaku untuk tadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.14,0:08:41.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kau menemukan sesuatu?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.52,0:08:42.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Belum.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.89,0:08:46.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Roh dalam situasi yang sama\Ndengan Bu Izumi terlalu unik.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.61,0:08:48.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.44,0:08:53.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.11,0:08:55.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau dekat dengan Mizuha?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.53,0:08:57.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa kami hanya teman biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.95,0:08:59.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kapan dan di mana kalian bertemu?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.87,0:09:01.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Belum lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.91,0:09:03.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami punya teman yang sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.83,0:09:05.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.42,0:09:07.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini mungkin mengejutkanmu,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi sebaiknya kau menjauh darinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.75,0:09:11.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena dia itu jalang.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.51,0:09:12.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu "jalang"?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.97,0:09:15.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Jalang" adalah rubah betina.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.43,0:09:16.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu "rubah betina"?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.22,0:09:19.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seseorang yang akan merayu pria…
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.35,0:09:20.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu "merayu"?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.60,0:09:23.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Merayu" berarti…
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.85,0:09:26.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kujelaskan nanti.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.06,0:09:28.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.36,0:09:33.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.86,0:09:35.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia benar-benar ada, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.24,0:09:38.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bocah Buas, Senjata Serbaguna,\NUtusan Dewa, Fushi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.78,0:09:40.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia hebat.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.33,0:09:42.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sang legenda.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.83,0:09:45.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Boleh aku menyentuhmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.71,0:09:49.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sangat lembut dan hangat.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.71,0:09:53.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa bukti bahwa dia yang asli?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.30,0:09:57.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa janji takkan beri tahu siapa pun\Ntentang yang kau lihat atau dengar?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.39,0:10:00.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, lakukan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.31,0:10:05.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang kulihat?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.35,0:10:08.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini tidak nyata! Ini sesuatu yang gaib!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.94,0:10:11.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sulit kupercaya! Ini lezat!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.23,0:10:16.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak-anak zaman sekarang memang luar biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.78,0:10:19.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Matematika, kimia, dan olahraga.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.70,0:10:20.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.87,0:10:22.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika aku menuruti orang dewasa sombong itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.08,0:10:25.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,apa aku dapat hadiah?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, tapi siapa kau?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.75,0:10:28.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini Tonari.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia Prajurit Cahaya,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.33,0:10:31.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,teman Fushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.29,0:10:35.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Permisi, boleh kami bergabung
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.34,0:10:37.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,dengan klub apa pun ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.38,0:10:39.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, kami kelebihan kapasitas!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.68,0:10:41.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan langsung memutuskan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.60,0:10:44.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Apa salahnya, Wakil Ketua?\N- Kau bercanda? Kulaporkan guru!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.14,0:10:45.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Silakan saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.35,0:10:48.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak semua orang\Nbisa gabung Klub Riset Hal Gaib.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.19,0:10:51.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mizuha, kenapa kau tampak murung sekali?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.36,0:10:53.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika kau ingin bicara,\Nberi tahu aku kapan saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.57,0:10:56.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenang, aku baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.15,0:11:00.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan menyembunyikannya dariku.\NKita teman, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.70,0:11:04.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau tidak memakai aksesori rambut\Nyang kuberikan hari ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.91,0:11:07.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, aku lupa memakainya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.04,0:11:10.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika kau temanku, jangan lupa.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.21,0:11:16.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, aku akan pergi duluan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.80,0:11:18.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mizuha.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.05,0:11:20.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Senior!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.34,0:11:21.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga akan pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa di antara kalian?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.81,0:11:27.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan apa-apa.\NMungkin hanya suasana hatinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.60,0:11:28.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.89,0:11:32.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bolos kegiatan klub\Nhanya karena ingin!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.90,0:11:41.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.74,0:11:42.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.03,0:11:44.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tepat waktu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.45,0:11:46.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saki, kau sangat lamban.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tahu di mana Fushi?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.46,0:11:54.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mizuha…
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.84,0:11:56.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa? Apa itu mengganggumu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.34,0:11:59.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bilang mereka punya teman yang sama,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.72,0:12:02.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi, wajar jika mereka dekat.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bicara dengannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.26,0:12:04.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa dengan Funa? Dia belum datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.97,0:12:09.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.10,0:12:11.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa tidak?\NBukankah kalian selalu bersama?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.98,0:12:12.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sungguh, tidak ada apa-apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.98,0:12:19.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia datang ke sekolah hari ini…
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.11,0:12:22.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu lihat,\Nsuruh dia rajin ikut kegiatan klub.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.91,0:12:24.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.03,0:12:27.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya setiap kali dia absen tanpa alasan,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.28,0:12:30.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,entah bagaimana\Nkita akan dicurigai oleh guru.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.25,0:12:34.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pun tak paham alasannya\Nmenyalahkan Saki atas patah hatinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.17,0:12:36.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia suka melampiaskannya ke orang lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.50,0:12:38.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat anak kelas satu menginjak\Nserpihan bambu dan terluka,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia langsung menyalahkan\Norang di sampingnya…
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.38,0:12:44.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo pemanasan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.14,0:12:49.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau menonton acara kemarin?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.89,0:12:50.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Belum.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.81,0:12:52.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, aku merekamnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.37,0:13:15.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, kau menyukaiku?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.08,0:13:18.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak membencimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.34,0:13:22.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf soal hari ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.97,0:13:28.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak membahas ibumu\Nhanya karena kau tidak menyukainya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya mencemaskanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.52,0:13:33.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa. Aku tidak keberatan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.52,0:13:35.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.10,0:13:39.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masih ada banyak hal\Nyang tidak kupahami soal ibumu saat ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.48,0:13:42.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, aku akan mengawasinya\Ndemi memastikan kau tidak terluka.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.74,0:13:45.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.20,0:13:49.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mari kita lanjutkan yang tadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.87,0:13:51.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada orang yang kau sukai, Fushi?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.54,0:13:53.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.46,0:13:58.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa gadis berkulit gelap\Nbernama Tonari itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.83,0:14:00.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia manis sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.09,0:14:00.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.00,0:14:03.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Serta Yuki, Aiko, dan Kazumitsu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.46,0:14:06.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sangat menyukai\Nsemua orang di sekitarku.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.76,0:14:08.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, Messar agak sulit dihadapi.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.80,0:14:12.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga, kau mengejutkanku!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.76,0:14:15.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan itu maksudku dengan "suka".
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.35,0:14:17.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa mereka berpacaran?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.85,0:14:18.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berpacaran?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.44,0:14:22.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa aku tidak tahu soal ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.40,0:14:25.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenang. Mereka akan mendengar kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.19,0:14:27.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mustahil mereka bisa mendengar kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.49,0:14:30.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena kita juga tidak bisa\Nmendengar mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.03,0:14:31.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa mereka?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.95,0:14:34.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hairo dan Gugu.\NMereka tinggal bersama kami.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.24,0:14:35.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.54,0:14:37.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku melihatmu, jadi, aku mengikutimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.58,0:14:39.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ke sekolah memakai topeng itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.00,0:14:40.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.25,0:14:45.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pernah punya seseorang yang spesial?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seseorang yang spesial?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.01,0:14:50.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudku, kau pernah jatuh cinta?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.80,0:14:54.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, aku tidak tahu banyak\Ntentang topik ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.93,0:15:00.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sangat populer di sekolah hari ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.31,0:15:01.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Populer?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.61,0:15:05.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yakin banyak gadis\Nakan mengajakmu berkencan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.53,0:15:07.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tidak boleh menerimanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.74,0:15:09.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Berkencan"?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.49,0:15:11.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu hubungan sebelum menikah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.37,0:15:14.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, itu hubungan saat kau berciuman?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.41,0:15:16.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Messar selalu melakukan itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.50,0:15:20.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau hanya boleh berkencan\Ndengan orang yang kau sukai.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.21,0:15:21.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitukah?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.12,0:15:22.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan merahasiakannya dariku
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,jika kau punya hubungan seperti ini\Ndengan orang lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.67,0:15:30.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau yang memutuskan itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.72,0:15:32.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entah kenapa.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.18,0:15:38.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak berencana mengalami\Nhal seperti itu di masa depan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.31,0:15:40.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak yakin apa itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.85,0:15:45.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi dari buku dan melihat orang lain,\Naku tahu itu sesuatu yang penting.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.65,0:15:48.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meskipun aku mengalaminya,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.61,0:15:52.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,itu akan kehilangan maknanya\Nseiring hidupku yang panjang.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.70,0:15:55.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu perasaan yang tidak nyaman, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.70,0:15:59.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski menyukai seseorang,\Nkau tidak akan memacarinya?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.25,0:16:01.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak berdaya mengubah apa pun,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.92,0:16:03.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi, sebaiknya aku diam.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.29,0:16:07.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,\Njika aku mengajakmu berkencan,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.25,0:16:08.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau akan bagaimana?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.30,0:16:12.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja aku akan melakukan\Nyang baru saja kukatakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.80,0:16:15.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak akan mengencani siapa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.60,0:16:20.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika gadis yang menyukaimu ada di sisimu,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.73,0:16:23.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,apa yang bisa dia lakukan\Nuntuk membuatmu bahagia?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.40,0:16:25.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan bahagia selama dia\Ntidak melakukan apa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.19,0:16:32.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.75,0:16:41.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aura mereka manis sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.87,0:16:42.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aoki.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.83,0:16:46.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa hubungan mereka\Ntidak seperti yang kau pikirkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.54,0:16:49.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa dasar pemikiranmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.34,0:16:51.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika mereka berkencan,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.51,0:16:53.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,menurutmu mereka mungkin lebih mesra
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.34,0:16:55.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,di kuil begini,\Nyang tak didatangi siapa pun.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.68,0:16:59.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau tidak tanya Mizuha langsung?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.77,0:17:01.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak perlu cemas akan menyakitinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.73,0:17:02.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kumpulkan keberanianmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.06,0:17:05.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pria bernyali jauh lebih menarik!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.82,0:17:11.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau benar! Aku akan melakukan itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.11,0:17:14.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat makan!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Senior. Senior.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pacar. Pacar.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.95,0:17:21.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau harus tanya!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.91,0:17:23.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gugu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.16,0:17:25.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak ada yang komentar\Nsoal topengmu di sekolah, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.96,0:17:27.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.46,0:17:29.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu rupanya. Itu bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.09,0:17:30.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beri tahu aku jika ada masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.88,0:17:32.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau tidak ke dokter?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Operasi plastik populer belakangan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.01,0:17:36.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau harus memikirkannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.93,0:17:39.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita tak pernah tahu kapan alkohol\Ndi perutmu bisa meledakkan organmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.01,0:17:44.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hairo juga bisa ke dokter gigi\Ndan memasang gigi palsu baru.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.56,0:17:45.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sangat tertarik.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,March juga ingin melakukan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.19,0:17:50.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bermain di pasir menyenangkan,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.15,0:17:53.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi aku ingin bisa\Nlebih membantu semua orang.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.86,0:17:57.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah mengatur seseorang\Nuntuk menyekolahkanmu dan Iddy di rumah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.87,0:17:59.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekolah di rumah?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, aku menantikannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.87,0:18:04.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kai, kau sudah memutuskan\Ningin bekerja apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.50,0:18:07.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya, aku ingin\Npunya bengkel sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.37,0:18:09.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak tahu apa rencanamu,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.29,0:18:11.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi kita tak punya uang sebanyak itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.38,0:18:14.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan khawatir.\NYayasan akan berikan dukungan finansial.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.05,0:18:17.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, aku berangkat ke sekolah!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.76,0:18:21.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hati-hati di jalan, Mizuha.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.51,0:18:22.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku berangkat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.93,0:18:24.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hati-hati dengan mobil.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.89,0:18:26.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.19,0:18:31.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada yang aneh\Ndengan ibu palsu Mizuha.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.36,0:18:34.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya dia bisa\Ntenang ke sekolah hari ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.32,0:18:37.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dunia masih damai.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.95,0:18:40.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ke mana Fu pergi?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.12,0:18:42.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga tidak melihatnya kemarin pagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.28,0:18:43.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,March sangat khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.66,0:18:45.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenang, aku masih di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.00,0:18:47.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pergi ke mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.33,0:18:48.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pergi jalan-jalan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.54,0:18:51.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bilang kau pergi ke rumah Mizuha?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.54,0:18:53.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sungguh? Fushi, kau memang hebat.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.84,0:18:54.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benarkah itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.88,0:18:58.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kusarankan jangan terlibat
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.55,0:19:00.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,dengan gadis itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.22,0:19:02.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.89,0:19:04.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini untuk anak-anak perempuan.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.02,0:19:07.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Suvenir untuk kalian juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.94,0:19:09.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku anak perempuan!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.60,0:19:11.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau memenangkan uang pacuan kuda?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.31,0:19:12.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku merasa tidak enak.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.56,0:19:14.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shochu ini lumayan enak.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.48,0:19:15.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Paman Messar.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau punya sesuatu untuk kami?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.95,0:19:20.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang kalian mau?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Topi dengan pinggiran.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.49,0:19:22.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepeda.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.53,0:19:25.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Belilah sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.45,0:19:28.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sikapmu dingin ke orang yang lebih muda.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.42,0:19:32.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Era ini tidak terlalu buruk.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.58,0:19:36.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan musnahnya Nokker,\Naku merasa dicintai oleh dunia ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.09,0:19:39.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Silakan.\N- Silakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.51,0:19:43.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, di sini damai lagi hari ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.01,0:19:46.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.10,0:19:47.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo ke sekolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.19,0:19:53.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Mizuha.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.48,0:19:56.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuki, kau datang pagi sekali hari ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.86,0:20:01.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau punya pacar?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.45,0:20:06.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya penasaran.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.37,0:20:08.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak perlu bilang jika tak mau.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.45,0:20:09.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku punya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar. Tentu saja punya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.83,0:20:13.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana mungkin kau tak punya pacar?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.92,0:20:15.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana sikapmu jika itu jawabanku?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku… Aku pasti mendukungmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.84,0:20:23.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.64,0:20:27.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang kau lakukan jika jatuh cinta\Npada gadis yang tak menyukaimu?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.14,0:20:32.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika itu kau, apa yang akan kau lakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.15,0:20:35.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.40,0:20:39.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.\NSebaliknya, itu pasti merepotkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.07,0:20:41.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang akan kau lakukan\Njika seseorang bilang begitu padamu?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.78,0:20:47.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku berpura-pura tidak mendengarnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.95,0:20:53.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebaliknya, aku mungkin merasa sedih.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.92,0:20:55.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.08,0:20:57.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti perasaanmu, Yuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.84,0:21:00.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mengerti?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.34,0:21:02.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga akan lakukan yang terbaik,\Njadi, mari berusaha bersama.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.97,0:21:03.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.88,0:21:05.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang kalian lakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.64,0:21:09.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hanna, kau pakai aksesori rambut\Nbuatanku hari ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.60,0:21:11.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mizuha hanya gadis biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.98,0:21:14.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau melarangku terlibat dengannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.48,0:21:17.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, dia tampak normal.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.11,0:21:19.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hayase, Hisame, dan Kahaku
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.44,0:21:20.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,juga tampak normal awalnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.19,0:21:24.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, dia mungkin akan kembali\Nuntuk menghantuimu suatu hari nanti.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.66,0:21:27.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti kegelisahanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.91,0:21:30.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, Nokker sudah musnah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.20,0:21:31.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.25,0:21:33.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.54,0:21:37.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku melihatmu bertarung di kursi itu\Nselama ratusan tahun.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.71,0:21:39.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari-hari itu sangat membosankan,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.59,0:21:42.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,menunggumu,\Ntanpa tahu kapan kau akan bangun.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.88,0:21:47.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi bagaimana kalau seperti sebelumnya,\Nsegala di dalam dirimu direnggut lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.30,0:21:50.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mau Bon bunuh diri lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.85,0:21:52.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Takkan kubiarkan itu terulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.02,0:21:54.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena Kahaku gagal mencapai era modern,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.06,0:21:56.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,kau memanfaatkan gadis itu\Ndemi mengisi kekosongan?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.98,0:21:59.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau menganggap Kahaku\Nsebagai teman lamamu, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.86,0:22:01.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak keberatan.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.28,0:22:06.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kau tak meremehkan ini hanya karena\NMarch berpikir ini baik-baik saja, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.20,0:22:09.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika March itu sosok dewasa,\Ndia mungkin akan berpikir berbeda.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.49,0:22:13.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seperti, "Kenapa kau berteman\Ndengan orang yang membunuhku?"
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.70,0:22:16.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau bilang begitu?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.42,0:22:17.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semua Nokker sudah kuhabisi.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.96,0:22:20.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain itu, tidak ada Nokker\Ndi dalam tubuh Mizuha.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.59,0:22:25.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya ingin memastikan\Ndunia ini benar-benar damai.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.26,0:22:28.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena kita akan hidup,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.64,0:22:30.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,lalu perlahan mati di dunia ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.93,0:22:34.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.10,0:22:36.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah itu alasanmu\Nmenghidupkan kami kembali?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.64,0:22:38.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bilang kau tak memikirkannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.77,0:22:39.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.36,0:22:43.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tonari, akan kubuktikan padamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.11,0:22:46.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dunia ini adalah surga\Nyang selalu kau inginkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:32.09,0:24:36.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kota yang tampak damai\Nmenyembunyikan bayangan meresahkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:37.68,0:24:42.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bon menemukan petunjuk tentang Nokker\Nyang bersembunyi di dalam manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:43.98,0:24:46.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang muncul di hadapan Fushi
Dialogue: 10,0:24:47.36,0:24:49.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,adalah seorang gadis muda dan…
Dialogue: 10,0:24:49.99,0:24:51.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu…
